.name
PPrefs
.author
Olaf Gschweng 
.version
1.1
.description
A screen mode promotion utility, Features: supports general screen
promotion rules; keeps lists of exceptions (screens and tasks); exceptions
could be promoted differently or kept; can use BestModeID() under 3.0 to
determine best suitable screen mode (offers some options to control);
preferences editor with font-sensitive, localized GUI; saves preferences to
IFF file.  
